Hai Everyone,
    
Steps to Run this Program:
    
    1. Run Your Xen Hypervisior(as i done this for xen Hypervisor)
    2. Install libvirt package libvirt-dev(supports : QEMU, KVM, XEN, OpenVZ, LXC, and VirtualBox).
    3. In terminal Compile the code by giving:
            
                gcc -g yourprogram.c -o target_object_file.o -lvirt   
    4. Run Your Object Code and all is Done. 

Thank You
